high_descs: Walk forward to the white table.
Pick up the yellow apple from the table.
Turn right, turn right again, cross room to refrigerator, turn left to face the refrigerator.
Put apple in refrigerator, close door, open door take apple out
Turn left, turn left, turn right, cross room to white table, turn right to face black table.
Put apple to right of other apple on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put an apple on black table.

high_descs: Go forward to face the white table straight ahead.
Take the apple off of the table.
Go right and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge and then close the door, open the door and take the apple out and shut the door again.
Turn to the left and go straight ahead and turn right towards the little black table at the end of the counter.
Put the apple on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple on a table.

high_descs: Pick up the apple that's in front of you.
Turn around and walk to the fridge that's to your left and turn left to face it.
Chill the apple in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the table then turn right and take a tiny step back.
Put this apple to the right of the other apple.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold apple on the table.
